心靈魂最大的試煉。<br />\n　　香港的未來如何，甚至香港還有沒有未來，就看我們是要擁抱理性，還是被恐懼和不信任擊敗！<br />\n本書特色"},{"pid":"d1c8e66627b98e62d9648c4aa1e1ba623813a3db","tid":1695644,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce5cd9ced665dc849f54d2bf346dba6bd615585","tid":1695644,"uid":167634,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"醫院係咪有後備電源？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:27:05.000Z","msg":"醫院牛房有genset<br />\n係可以頂到一陣既"},{"pid":"590959a4946172e3d210fde773d5121de4d4e905","tid":1695644,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:33:25.000Z","msg":"會無直播<br />\n變成翻版64<br />\n無死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7172b1cc94ef912bc4d5382e4cf31971024f2b72","tid":1695644,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:34:32.000Z","msg":"搞左黨鐵果啲牛房制房先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如長沙灣A1出口隔壁果座traction substation"},{"pid":"519be908646ac8ed265ff830cc62e8ceaa889fa2","tid":1695644,"uid":36915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:35:06.000Z","msg":"你控制到中電又典<br />\n到時比人標籤係恐佈份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e475ea49dcedda2e3d3b575a54ec6e51d9399291","tid":1695644,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:43:09.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師會死哂<br />\n燈神燒山無電著燈"},{"pid":"d896ed92d28a8c7ae46468539dc4dfa1d9829bc5","tid":1695644,"uid":69688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:46:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會有病人唔喺醫院住<br />\n但係需要用電嘅野維生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"b381847b73f43beb4d1390871913dda083f63796","tid":1695644,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:52:2